        <h3 id="overview">Health Issues Mapping -&gt; FHIR Profiles (CZ PS)</h3>

        <p>
            Below is a browsable diagram showing how the Health Issues model is realized by the HL7 FHIR profiles defined in this guide. The mapping covers all aspects of health problems, procedures, medical devices, and functional status assessment.
        </p>

        <h4 id="model">Model Overview</h4>
        <p>{% include PS_HealthIssues-map.svg %}</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
            <strong>Mapping Context</strong>

            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Source logical model:</strong>
                    <a href="StructureDefinition-LogHealthIssuesCzEn.html">LogHealthIssuesCzEn</a>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <strong>Main target profile:</strong>
                    <a href="StructureDefinition-cz-composition-ps.html">cz-composition-ps</a>
                </li>

            </ul>

        </div>

